Add game object events, WebSocket keepalive, and navigate_item resilience
- Emit type:"action" events for GAME_OBJECT interactions (POH furniture,
  altars, portals) with target/option/objectId for investment savings tracking
- Add ~50s keepalive pings to prevent Cloudflare idle timeout disconnects
- Improve navigate_item: detect dead sockets and trigger reconnect instead
  of silently failing; fall back to browser open when relay unavailable


